description:
The manual field is being replaced by awaiting=work. Implement backwards compatibility:

Reading ticks:
```go
func (t *Task) IsAwaitingHuman() bool {
    if t.Awaiting != "" {
        return true
    }
    return t.Manual  // backwards compat
}

func (t *Task) GetAwaitingType() string {
    if t.Awaiting != "" {
        return t.Awaiting
    }
    if t.Manual {
        return "work"
    }
    return ""
}
```

Writing ticks:
- When setting awaiting, clear manual field
- When reading manual=true with no awaiting, treat as awaiting=work

Query filters:
- Check both awaiting and manual fields when filtering

Acceptance criteria:
- [ ] Old ticks with manual=true work correctly
- [ ] New ticks use awaiting field only
- [ ] Queries filter on both fields for backwards compat
- [ ] No data migration required (reads both, writes new)
